      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">A documented risk assessment and/or a job safety analysis must be completed by a trained person prior to using any lifting device.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Operators must be trained on the lifting equipment or cranes being operated. Training must be documented and available upon request.</li>
